These are Puzzles for 6x2 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 6x2-Level-1-1::.
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: ice-hockey, surfing
The people have 2 different jobs:  accountant, journalist
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: funk, pop
There are 2 different nationalities: french, malaysian
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: november, july
The people use 2 different means of transport: roller, van
1. the person who's birthday is in july is on the far left##1
2. the accountant is on the right of the person driving the roller##1
3. the person who's sport is surfing is on the far right##1
4. the french is on the right of the fan of pop##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |
| Sport      | ice-hockey       | surfing    |
| Job           | journalist | accountant |
| Music-Genre   | pop     | funk   |
| Nationality   | malaysian  | french     |
| Birthday           | july       | november     |
| Transport     | roller     | van        |

