.:: Puzzle 6x2-Level-1-2::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: 7up, water
The people have 2 different hobbies: camping, filmmaking
There are 2 different nationalities: nigerian, japanese
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: folk, pop
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: begonia, poppy
City: san-francisco, liverpool
1. the fan of pop is on the right of the person who growspoppy##1
2. the person drinking water is the fan of pop##1
3. the nigerian is on the left of the person who's hobby is camping##1
4. the person traveling to san-francisco is on the left of the person who growsbegonia##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |
| Beverage      | 7up        | water   |
| Hobby         | filmmaking | camping |
| Nationality   | nigerian     | japanese   |
| Music-Genre   | folk       | pop     |
| Flower           | poppy        | begonia    |
| City     | san-francisco  | liverpool    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 6x2-Level-1-3::.
