The people have 2 different hobbies: baking, writing
House: ranch-style, cape-cod
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: march, august
2 different pets are kept: cat, guinea-pig
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: iris, poppy
1. the owner of the cat is on the left of the person who's hobby is baking##1
2. the ranch-style house is on the right of the person eating pepper##1
3. the person who's birthday is in august is on the left of the person who growsiris##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2       |
| Food          | pepper    | avocado      |
| Hobby         | writing   | baking       |
| House   | cape-cod | ranch-style |
| Birthday   | august  | march    |
| Pet           | cat       | guinea-pig   |
| Flower         | poppy   | iris     |

