.:: Puzzle 6x2-Level-1-6::.
There 2 different types of food: potato, spinach
The people have 2 different hobbies: chess, hiking
2 different games are played: monopoly, bridge
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: adventure, horror
The people use 2 different means of transport: quad-bike, jet-ski
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: dunhill, aristoff
1. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the left of the aristoff-smoker##1
2. the dunhill-smoker is on the left of the person driving the jet-ski##1
3. the person watching adventure movies is the person playing monopoly##1
4. the person eating potato is on the left of the person watching adventure movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |
| Food          | potato     | spinach   |
| Hobby         | hiking     | chess     |
| Game           | bridge   | monopoly   |
| Movie-Genre   | horror     | adventure |
| Transport   | quad-bike | jet-ski   |
| Cigar   | dunhill  | aristoff    |

